===Noun===
{{en-noun|worry|worries}}
# A strong [[feeling]] of anxiety.
#:''I'm afflicted by '''worry''' throughout the night.''
# An instance or cause of such a feeling
#:''My main '''worry''' is that I'll miss the train.''

